@startuml
actor "Quản lý / Admin" as Manager
participant "Browser (tasks.html)" as Frontend
participant "TaskController" as APIController
participant "TaskService" as Service
database "Database" as DB

Manager -> Frontend : Điền form & Nhấn "Lưu"
Frontend -> APIController : POST /api/tasks (JSON: CreateTaskRequest)
APIController -> Service : createTask(req)
Service -> DB : Tạo mới Task (Status: PENDING)
DB --> Service : OK
Service --> APIController : Trả về TaskDTO
APIController --> Frontend : HTTP 201 Created (JSON)
Frontend -> Manager : Hiển thị "Giao việc thành công"
Frontend -> Frontend : Cập nhật bảng Kanban
@enduml
